<ab><del rend="overstrike">fifes like a tho</del> the thousand whistles of the fifes, (playing Lannigan's ball) so <del rend="overstrike">ro</del> with inexpressible roguishness—(50 drums)</ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-long-left"/>

<ab>the Irish with their heads all <del rend="overstrike">d</del> copiously dressed with branches of green—impulsive, shouting—</ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>

<ab>President, Gen. Grant, Stanton Meade, Hancock Sec Wells, McCulloch

<pb xml:id="leaf003v" facs="uva.00062.006.jpg" type="verso"/>

—some of the very full artillery regts <subst><del rend="ovewrwrite" seq="1"><gap reason="illegible" extent="one letter" quantity="1" unit="chars"/></del><add rend="unmarked" place="over" seq="2">l</add></subst>ook'd splendidly—moving in masses—

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>

good, hearty young men</ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-long-left"/>

<ab>scene near President's stand—rolling drums saluting officers</ab>
<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-long-left"/>

<pb xml:id="leaf004r" facs="uva.00062.007.jpg" type="recto"/>
