<ab>—the pontoons</ab>
<ab>—the big panniers on mules backs fill'd with shovels 
<add place="right" rend="insertion">(panniers made of ox-hide)</add></ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>

<ab>9th Corps—splendid</ab>
<ab>—with battle flags</ab>
<ab>—men looked very neat &amp; clean but worn</ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>

<ab>with bouquets in caps</ab>
<ab>—the ambulance with hanging lantern</ab>
 
<pb xml:id="leaf007v" facs="uva.00062.009.jpg" type="verso"/>

<pb xml:id="leaf008r" facs="uva.00062.010.jpg" type="recto"/>

<ab>great drum corps</ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>

<ab>old tatters, that had been battle flags</ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-full"/>

<ab>Pioneers with axes on shoulders</ab>

<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>

<ab>the crowds</ab>
<ab>the perfect day—the clear sky—the white, &amp; edged clouds</ab>
</div1>

